<plot>A shopping center of the Bernese suburbs organizes the election of the «couple of the year». The winning couple gets trousseau and marriage. The wedding ceremony takes place within the shopping center. Ruse and negotiations, resistance and resignation, values and image: a promotional comedy? A journey into the land of appearances? What is real, what is faked?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?126993</url></doc>
